say { "unicorn";
	glance %n;
	say unicorn did you say, well if it's unicorn you seek, I can be of aid!;
	shake %n;
	say Let me introduce myself, I'm Jacob Swindlestick, the one, the only,;
	say unicorn tracker.  I'm sure you've heard of me, haven't you?;
	arch %n;
	say well no matter, no matter, let's get down to <r>business<1> then, shall we?;
        }

say { "business";
        say Ahh, my favorite word that!  Now I'm sure you've heard all about this;
	say Unicorn business, virgins and all that, utter nonsense, I myself have;
	say visited many a unicorn, and I can say, nothing special, nothing at all.;
	say Except of course.. well I'm not sure I should tell you, trade secrets and all.;
	say But, you look like a nice person, so I'll let you in on this amazing secret.;
	say <r>Urine<1>.;
        }

say { "urine";
        nod;
	say Yes, amazing stuff, that unicorn urine!  Why I use it for everything!;
	say It'll make your teeth whiter, your hair shorter, and strip the rust right off that ..;
	say well never mind that, what I've got here is a limited supply of clarified urine.;
	tell %n And of course, the clarified urine is even better!;
	tell %n Mind you this is a limited supply, and it's going to cost you some, but my friend,;
	tell %n It is worth so much more then mere money, just think of all you'll gain.;
	tell %n Why you'll be the first one on your block with GENUINE clarified unicorn urine!;
	tell %n It's not everyday you can call home about that!;
	tell %n And since I think your such a nice guy, I could part with some of this exceedingly rare;
	tell %n urine for the LOW, LOW price of  #OBJCOST( 31309, 60)# talens!;
        }

say {"component";
	link say unicorn;
    }

give { "-#OBJCOST( 31309, 60)#";
        load 31309;
        toroom $n reaches into his pants and pulls out a tiny vial with some incredibly clear liquid inside.;
	toroom $n hold the vial up to the light, nodding slowly.;
	say Yes, yes, a perfect sample.;
	sigh;
	say Well I'll be sad to see this go, quite rare and valuable!;
	say I'm sure I can get more though.;
	grin;
	say Come back if you ever need more!;
        give urine %n;
       	say Enjoy the urine my friend, it's been a pleasure doing business with you!;
	toroom $n fingers the now bulging money purse on his hip, a blissful look on his face.;
        }
